Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.35,0:00:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've come, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.73,0:00:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(642,544)}Chris... No, V!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.31,0:00:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! How could you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.70,0:00:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.18,0:00:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They haven't been broadcasting the Duels this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Yuma okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.21,0:00:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.36,0:00:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito-{\i1}sama{\i0}! I can't stay put any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.63,0:00:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he turns me into scrap, I will stay by Kaito-{\i1}sama{\i0}'s side!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.53,0:00:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am his humble tool!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the heck are we even riding to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.45,0:00:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, slow down a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.67,0:00:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I gotta hurry and find someone who can fight me in the one-on-one Duels!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That may be true, but even\N if you blindly ride through the darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.20,0:01:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think's gonna happen\N if you fall into another Trap again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.10,0:01:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.47,0:01:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did someone fall into a Trap?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.27,0:01:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Humble tool...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.92,0:01:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orbital?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.53,0:01:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh~! You're the source of humbleness!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.35,0:01:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you okay? You're not broken, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.52,0:01:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.06,0:01:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes! You're that dreadful scrap woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.32,0:01:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, I'm gonna throw you off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.50,0:01:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gah! Hold on a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.48,0:01:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to hurry to Kaito-{\i1}sama{\i0}'s side!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.87,0:01:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... I have something I need to tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.99,0:01:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orbital! Show me the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.65,0:02:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.77,0:02:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always knew the day would \Ncome where we would fight each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.87,0:02:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On that day I learned the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.98,0:02:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was consumed by feelings of hatred and revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that day...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.33,0:02:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hurt Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you regret doing that! Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.28,0:02:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take the first turn. My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Planet Pathfinder!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I Special Summon Solar Wind Jammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.74,0:03:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card can be Special Summoned from my hand by halving its Attack Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I activate the Magic Card, Tannhäuser Gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card changes the levels of my two Monsters to the total of their combined levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Monsters are Level Four and Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, my two Monsters become Level Nines!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two Level Nine Monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Overlay the Level Nine Planet Pathfinder and Solar Wind Jammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.98,0:03:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use these two Monsters to build the Overlay Network.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.11,0:03:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xyz Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.39,0:03:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show yourself, Number 9!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Number!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.43,0:03:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.52,0:03:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sky Canopy Star - Dyson Sphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.21,0:04:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is your Number?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.98,0:04:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment I successfully Xyz Summoned,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.48,0:04:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because of the effect of the\N Field Magic activated here, Cosmic Frontier,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can draw one card!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.33,0:04:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one card face-down and end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.95,0:04:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is his Monster...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.48,0:04:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn, Kaito.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.39,0:04:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I can't see what it looks like,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.67,0:04:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}if he Summoned a Monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.15,0:04:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Photon Delta Wing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Photon Delta Wing, attack his Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Photon Missile!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately for you, your attacks won't be able to reach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Im-Impossible...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done now? Then I suppose it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.24,0:05:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.38,0:05:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use Dyson Sphere to attack Photon Delta Wing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.36,0:05:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't know, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.51,0:05:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My current Dueling goes far beyond your comprehension.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Advance, advance, beyond the limits of your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.13,0:05:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come along with me and burn our flame of life
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, my friends, what scenery do you suppose
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}awaits us on the other side of this hill?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.62,0:06:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, my friends, let's climb it together
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's too late for us to turn back now
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The time has come to combine\N together the power dwelling inside me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.30,0:06:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gotta release my Soul Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.89,0:06:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Advance, advance, beyond the limits of your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.11,0:06:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come along with me and burn our flame of life
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.49,0:06:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep running, keep running, until you get there
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:07:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Once again, once again, keep those challenges coming
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.16,0:07:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My friends, keep on living in the here and now
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.54,0:07:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep pressing onward together no matter what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.44,0:07:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this is amazing! Is this space?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(549,510)}"Number 55: Galaxy Eyes Sealed?!\N The Cosmic Class Number Appears!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.52,0:07:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This appears to be the Space Field.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll confirm the verification signal on the D-Pad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(670,515)}It's Kaito-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.81,0:07:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,528)}On that space ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(682,531)}H-Hold on! You're going too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(632,518)}B-Because this thing won't do what I tell it to!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.98,0:07:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you really are an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you harmed, Kaito-{\i1}sama{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You people...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito, I have something I need to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.99,0:08:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.91,0:08:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Droite... During Droite's Duel...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Tron jerk took her down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Droite... fought desperately against Tron for your sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.87,0:08:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.29,0:08:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Droite liked y-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's none of my concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.24,0:08:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.52,0:08:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito-{\i1}sama{\i0}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.84,0:08:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.34,0:08:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma Tsukumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuma-{\i1}san{\i0}'s son.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think all the actors would gather in one place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This could very well be the act of fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something I want to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.81,0:09:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad... Where's my dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. Before this Duel unfolds,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall tell you all that I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop joking around! I don't want to listen to anything you have to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.38,0:09:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's continue the Duel already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito, this story is related to you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think our family appeared in this Duel Carnival?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And why do you supposed we went after you siblings?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we seek revenge against your father, Dr. Faker?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.56,0:09:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Dr. Faker is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Faker is Kaito's dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you guys want revenge against him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck does he mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.01,0:09:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad and Kaito's dad were...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll know the answer once you hear this story.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Five years ago from this date...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A scientist as well as Kaito's father, Faker,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,spent a great amount of time researching a way to open the door to the Parallel Worlds with my father, Byron.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am observing distortions in the dimensions all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And despite that, why can't I specify its location?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why can't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Faker...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come drink this and calm your nerve-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have no time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.05,0:10:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't find the door to the Parallel Worlds soon...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Faker...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.65,0:10:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's someone else looking for the door to the Parallel Words other than us...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chris, bring up that image.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.03,0:10:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's quite the interesting person with considerable talent, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.55,0:10:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A man who is an adventurer, Kazuma Tsukumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is nice. I can take it easy for a while here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No one will bother me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.29,0:11:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.38,0:11:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well... Guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.57,0:11:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wow, that's some impressive equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm grateful that you came all the way here when we called you on such short notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.75,0:11:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kazuma Tsukumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am Byron Arclight. I am in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A Gravity Charter Electromagnetic Wave Map, huh? That's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is no time for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.18,0:11:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have investigated all the phenomenon that has been occurring!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I haven't been able to find anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Something... Something's missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kazuma, will you give us your opinion on
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.75,0:11:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}all of our research regarding the Parallel Worlds, whether we're right or wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:11:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we find that door, the history of mankind will be changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.61,0:12:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet we'll get more wealth \Nand fame than we'd ever think imaginable!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wealth and fame...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have no need for such worthless nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.40,0:12:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to find the door to the Parallel Worlds at all costs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.97,0:12:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hearing that puts my mind at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.81,0:12:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kazuma! You...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The only thing I'm interested in is genuine adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So you were testing us...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.80,0:12:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.58,0:12:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we want the door to the Parallel Worlds to open itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.88,0:12:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}we have to observe any unusual behavior within the 21 passage points that are invoked on the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.62,0:12:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we analyze them, I suspect we will be able to specify where the next door will manifest itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.86,0:12:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A 21 formulaic equation, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.39,0:12:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right. The answer has already begun to reveal itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.37,0:12:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm just one step away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But that one step is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.47,0:12:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It won't appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:12:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:13:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Absurd...! All of the observations are...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.72,0:13:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The location isn't within 21 passage points.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There are some things you just can't understand in a lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.84,0:13:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's still two passage points remaining. In other words, there's 23 points where occurrence is possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-Is that... really true!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.31,0:13:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes. The answer is that this is really a 23 formulaic equation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.21,0:13:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, we began gathering new information in order to calculate a new formula.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We reached a single conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.02,0:13:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the place we were headed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was the location where we believed the next door to the Parallel Worlds would reveal itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, our adventure begins now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.54,0:13:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You guys will wait here and be on standby.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It will just be us going from here on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just the three of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll be okay. Don't worry, Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.46,0:13:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw nothing beyond this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened after is what my father told me from his memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.44,0:14:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuma-{\i1}san{\i0} guided the three of them down the mountain toward the bottom of the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kazuma-{\i0}san{\i1}, do you really think we'll be able to get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our destination is unprecedented territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But that is why there's meaning in taking up the challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.63,0:14:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1} We gotta bring it to 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bring it to 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.47,0:14:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's the feeling to never give up on a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.83,0:14:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is that a picture of your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.60,0:14:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The boy's obsessed with Dueling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.18,0:14:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oho, my family as well.\N We have three sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.91,0:15:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Faker also has two sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.24,0:15:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why is Dr. Faker so concerned with all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.18,0:15:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not sure, but Faker is a true genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He must be thinking about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.06,0:15:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As for me, no matter what it takes,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to help him find the door of the Parallel Worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.22,0:15:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dr. Faker must be happy to have such a good friend like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good friend, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"When two souls are offered up, the door shall open."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I figured.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.95,0:15:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three days after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father and the others finally reached their destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.37,0:15:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are these some kind of historic ruins?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could this be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is! I can't be wrong! This is the Parallel World's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.13,0:16:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If that's the case, the door to the Parallel Worlds must be up ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.39,0:16:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Faker! Kazuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.04,0:16:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see. In order to keep out intruders, they've set all sorts of traps in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.69,0:16:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We haven't even seen the real threats yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.01,0:16:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those without wisdom and courage\N shouldn't dare to step foot in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.71,0:16:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you all right, Faker?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.97,0:16:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Strange. There has to be something here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.11,0:17:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.75,0:17:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.16,0:17:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This moment has come at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Faker!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.93,0:17:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hold no hatred toward either of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.74,0:17:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the hell are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is something written on the ground below your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It says, "When two souls are offered up, the door shall open."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You don't... intend to sacrifice us!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Faker!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.12,0:17:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I must find the door to the Parallel Worlds no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dr. Faker! Wasn't Byron your close friend!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.53,0:17:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Close friend? What nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you call yourself my close friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}you should be delighted to become my sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.98,0:17:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Byron!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:17:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Faker!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.65,0:18:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After all, mediocre fools like you couldn't possibly understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm gonna Bring it to 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.77,0:18:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kazuma... Kazuma, let go of my hand!\N If you don't, you'll also...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a bit inappropriate and childish for this situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.24,0:18:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but people say if you Duel, you're sure to make friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dueling and adventuring is the same to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.57,0:18:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you adventure together with others, you'll all become friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.64,0:18:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kazuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't ever give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now disappear from my sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.36,0:18:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll never forget this grudge, Faker!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.75,0:18:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how my dad met his end...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.24,0:18:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"If you offer up two souls, a new door shall be opened."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.23,0:19:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is... Xyz Summoning!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my father came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}While wandering the threshold in the Parallel Worlds, he fed off his own thoughts for revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, his appearance began\N to change greatly as compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.79,0:19:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Into the form you see now of my father, Tron!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.15,0:19:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What'd you just say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.94,0:19:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tron... {\i1}That same{\i0} Tron is III and V's dad!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.73,0:19:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the one responsible for all of this is Dr. Faker!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will have retribution at all costs!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.29,0:19:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I live only for Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no interest in what he... Dr. Faker has done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.61,0:19:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're continuing the Duel! Move, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.28,0:19:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Special Summon Photon Thrasher!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.80,0:20:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card can be Special Summoned\N when I have no Monsters on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.59,0:20:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I Normal Summon Photon Pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Photon Pirate can Banish one Photon Monster in my Graveyard in order to raise this card's Attack Power by 1000 during this turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has two Monsters with over 2000 Attack Power on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.54,0:20:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito's about to play his trump card!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I release Photon Thrasher and Photon Pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darkness within the shining galaxy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.43,0:20:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Become the light of hope and live as my servant!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Embodiment of Light will now descend!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.26,0:20:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Appear before us! Galaxy Eyes Photon Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.37,0:20:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've appeared, Galaxy Eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.78,0:20:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the last turn, my 1800 Attack Power Delta Wing was destroyed and I received 1000 points of damage...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:21:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In other words, the invisible enemy has 2800 Attack Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.62,0:21:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll demolish it using the 3000 Attack Power Galaxy Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.71,0:21:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.03,0:21:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Photon Stream of Destruction!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.46,0:21:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.18,0:21:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, Kaito. I will show you my Number!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.95,0:21:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.59,0:21:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ridiculously huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.74,0:21:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.62,0:22:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Monster so very large that it enshrouds the very sun itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.85,0:22:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sky Canopy Star - Dyson Sphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.90,0:22:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No other Monster can even hope to defeat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.50,0:22:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We stand tall, until we have victory in our grasp
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.89,0:22:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Move on ahead, speeding up our throbbing beats
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.90,0:22:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen boys and girls, here's the secret to boys and girls like you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.36,0:22:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're really just so spontaneous, wild as can be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.24,0:22:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet you didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.78,0:22:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You might be a handful, but what's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.37,0:22:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be up to no good, but learn for real
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.00,0:22:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go the unpredictable route and shuffle your cards with a goal in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.25,0:23:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whenever you feel like you've lost your way, just take a minute to close your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.51,0:23:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shout "stop!" with all you've got, and there's your boundary line.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.39,0:23:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We stand tall, until we have victory in our grasp
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.69,0:23:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We won't just stop here, not when we don't want to have any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.19,0:23:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if we get hurt, we can't just hesitate now
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.49,0:23:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We won't just give up, not when our future's a lot brighter than our today
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.87,0:23:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seriousness... It'll only make us keep fighting even harder
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.33,0:23:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll always get as fascinated as we want, and we'll fight on every day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.93,0:23:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,V's Number is Dyson Sphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.74,0:23:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its ability protects it from all attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.03,0:23:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's truly an invincible Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.83,0:24:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding! Kaito's going to lose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.75,0:24:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's read through every one of his attacks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.75,0:24:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito... You're my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.55,0:24:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.88,0:24:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't allow you if you lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.63,0:24:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Yu-Gi-Oh! ZeXal!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.59,0:24:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Great Decisive Battle of Outer Space!\N Neo Galaxy-Eyes Strikes Back"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.93,0:24:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What {\i1}is{\i0} that card?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.89,0:24:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today we're introducing Number 9: Dyson Sphere!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.31,0:24:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How big it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.69,0:24:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose to its size!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.15,0:24:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the bathroom, I can make something {\i1}way{\i0} bigger-
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.07,0:24:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying when people are eating dinner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.32,0:24:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize...
